Module HW05
Package model

Interface IUpdateStrategyFac<TMsg>

  • Type Parameters:
    TMsg - The type of message that the supplied IDispatcher can send.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IUpdateStrategyFac.ErrorFactory, IUpdateStrategyFac.NullFactory
    public interface IUpdateStrategyFac<TMsg>
    An interface that defines a factory that instantiates a specific IUpdateStrategy.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static class  IUpdateStrategyFac.ErrorFactory<TMsg>
      A factory for a beeping error strategy that beeps the speaker every 25 updates.
      static class  IUpdateStrategyFac.NullFactory<TMsg>
      A factory for a typed null strategy object.
      Usage: instantiate this factory class using the desired TDispMsg type and then call its make() method to create the correctly typed null strategy object.
